&lt;p&gt;16 hours per week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is a flexible role designed to support all cleaning in the Trust Accommodation Buildings. This will comprise of 69 rooms, 39 Flats, and Communal areas. The post holder is a member of a team dedicated to providing and maintaining high standards of cleanliness in accordance with the Trust’s Standards of Cleanliness.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SPECIAL CONDITIONS: The first week on August is an extremely busy time in this role and for the Accommodation Department therefore there is an expectation that annual leave will not be taken at this time other than in exceptional circumstances.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sara Hickman, Senior Customer Services Officer&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address sara.hickman@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number 03033 302166&lt;/p&gt;
